Class SnapshotSessionNewTargetsParam

      • getCopyMode

        public java.lang.String getCopyMode()
        Get the copy mode for the new target volumes to be linked to the block snapshot session. A volume that is linked to a snapshot session using "copy" copy_mode and achieves the "copied" state will contain a full, usable copy of the snapshot session source device upon being unlinked from the session. This is not true for volumes linked in "nocopy" copy-mode. Valid values: copy nocopy
        Returns:
        The copy mode for the new target volumes to be linked to the block snapshot session.
